    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This is the <strong>second entry</strong> of a <strong>three-part </strong>horror series that blends <strong>exploration </strong>and<strong> claustrophobic horror</strong> </i>elements<i>. </i>This part includes <strong>three chapters</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018940/extras/3898d11c04729d8f62da681f358c6f71.poster.avif?t=1771962079\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018940/extras/3898d11c04729d8f62da681f358c6f71.webm?t=1771962079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018940/extras/3898d11c04729d8f62da681f358c6f71.mp4?t=1771962079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You continue the story as John Rand, a search-and-rescue officer stationed at Richburg National Park. After the events of Part 1, John faces new threats as he tries to make his way to Richburg Mines to rescue Michelle and Elena before it's too late.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018940/extras/48e7a1e50f22eff03d6835ed1dae6ac7.poster.avif?t=1771962079\" width=560 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018940/extras/48e7a1e50f22eff03d6835ed1dae6ac7.webm?t=1771962079\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3018940/extras/48e7a1e50f22eff03d6835ed1dae6ac7.mp4?t=1771962079\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Steam Achievements:</strong><